because you forgot your place.

01:12.806 --> 01:13.956
You're a creative person.

01:13.974 --> 01:15.892
You need to find
an artistic outlet.

01:15.926 --> 01:17.293
Come codirect the musical
with me.

01:17.311 --> 01:18.761
<i>Grease</i> was your idea.
I don't know

01:18.795 --> 01:20.263
