01:20.297 --> 01:21.814
Directing is
about having an idea

01:21.849 --> 01:23.466
and convincing everyone
around you to make it happen.

01:23.484 --> 01:24.567
I don't think so.

01:24.601 --> 01:25.985
Fine.

01:26.020 --> 01:27.970
Then I'm not doing it, either,

01:27.988 --> 01:29.489
