01:29.523 --> 01:31.774
You can't do that, man,
hold the musical hostage.

01:31.808 --> 01:33.142
That's like terrorism.

01:33.160 --> 01:35.678
Basically, Olivia Newton-John
is strapped to my chest,

01:35.713 --> 01:37.413
