codirect with me,

01:37.448 --> 01:38.498
I'm gonna blow her up.

01:39.366 --> 01:40.816
I'm serious, Finn.

01:40.834 --> 01:42.952
Trust me, as your friend,
you need to do this.

01:42.986 --> 01:44.337
Just so you can look
at the first month

01:44.371 --> 01:45.621
